  "detailed_description": "Bunny Mahjo is the classic tile-matching game but in new look and feel decorated in Asian style and with asian music.<br>Grab your friend and complete 25 different puzzle or your own ones created in Constuctor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.poster.avif?t=1762957365\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.webm?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.mp4?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle constructor</h2><br>Construct any puzzle you want and play it with a friend or alone. Share your puzzles with your friends using exchange room.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.poster.avif?t=1762957365\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.webm?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.mp4?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 2-players cooperative mode  - you can invite a friend to your game or join them via steam invitation<br>- cute little environment<br>- Leaderboard<br>- no defeats<br><br><br>Some rules for multiplayer part<br>- only host can choose the puzzle or start a new game<br>- both host and client can use hints and shuffle the tiles",
  "about_the_game": "Bunny Mahjo is the classic tile-matching game but in new look and feel decorated in Asian style and with asian music.<br>Grab your friend and complete 25 different puzzle or your own ones created in Constuctor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.poster.avif?t=1762957365\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.webm?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/cb791d54e106fa278b7597ecac35bf8b.mp4?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle constructor</h2><br>Construct any puzzle you want and play it with a friend or alone. Share your puzzles with your friends using exchange room.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.poster.avif?t=1762957365\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.webm?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968470/extras/a29739cacf7c9e93e941e5b5eb159ba5.mp4?t=1762957365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 2-players cooperative mode  - you can invite a friend to your game or join them via steam invitation<br>- cute little environment<br>- Leaderboard<br>- no defeats<br><br><br>Some rules for multiplayer part<br>- only host can choose the puzzle or start a new game<br>- both host and client can use hints and shuffle the tiles",
